     * @param timestamp     the timestamp to embed in the batch header (milliseconds since epoch)
     * @param producerId    the transactional producer id
     * @param producerEpoch the producer epoch
     * @param marker        the {@link EndTransactionMarker} describing the transaction outcome
     * @return an immutable {@link MemoryRecords} containing the end-transaction control batch
     */
    public static MemoryRecords withEndTransactionMarker(long timestamp, long producerId, short producerEpoch,
                                                         EndTransactionMarker marker) {
